  <brief_title>European Multicenter Study Radiofrequency (RF) Versus Cryo in Atrioventricular Nodal Reentry Tachycardia (AVNRT)</brief_title>
  <official_title>European Multicenter Study RF Versus Cryo in AVNRT: A Randomized Study Comparing Cryo-Energy vs. Radiofrequency-Energy Ablation Technique for AV Nodal Reentry Tachycardia (AVNRT)</official_title>
